headline: Trading touchdowns: Robinhood launches Super Bowl prediction contracts
summary: Robinhood is rolling out event contracts to let U.S. users wager on the outcome of the Super Bowl clash, it said on Monday, seeking to tap into the betting mania around one of the most iconic sporting...
